        {
            "+content": "The world is laid to waste after the apocalypse. A new kind of hero begins to show himself to the people. With his \"Fist of the North Star\" technique, a man named Kenshiro slaughters those who would do violence on the innocent. He aims to violently set justice back in the world, and dreams of one day reuniting with his beloved, Julia.",
